While you are articulate Robin, that doesn't conceal the fact that you are taking things out of context and/or not facing the facts.  Stating that Shintou's position exhibited intolerance was NOT a personal attack.  You're likening my statements to a cross-examination whereby a defense attorney attempts to discredit a witness by giving examples, which have nothing to do with the particular incident, of poor character.<br>
<br>
Yes, I commented that Shin's position was intolerant.  Shintou stated:<br>
<br>
&quot;Roleplayers and Non Roleplayers are two different animals. Completly Different.<br>
<br>
You can't have Males in the Female Bathroom, it just doesn't work.<br>
It just doesn't work.<br>
<br>
Get off our server.&quot;<br>
